msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Jika anda berada di luar AS, kami mengesyorkan NOWPayments (yuran paling "
"rendah, terus ke dompet anda). Jika anda berada di AS, Stripe Crypto juga "
"merupakan pilihan. Anda boleh mengaktifkan beberapa perkhidmatan dan "
"membenarkan pengunjung anda memilih!"

msgid "Enabled Payment Methods"
msgstr "Kaedah Bayaran Dibolehkan"

msgid ""
"Select which payment options will appear in your widget. Your visitors can "
"choose their preferred method."
msgstr ""
"Pilih pilihan pembayaran yang akan dipaparkan di widget anda. Pengunjung "
"anda boleh memilih kaedah yang mereka sukai."

