"NOWPayments allows you to accept credit card payments directly to your "
"crypto wallet. Funds go straight to your wallet – no middleman."
msgstr ""
"NOWPayments membolehkan anda menerima pembayaran kad kredit terus ke dompet "
"crypto anda. Dana akan terus ke dompet anda – tiada pihak ketiga."

