"Stripe Crypto payments (USDC) are ONLY available for US-based businesses. If"
" you are outside the US, Stripe will only accept credit card payments to "
"your Stripe balance (not directly to crypto)."
msgstr ""
"Pembayaran Crypto Stripe (USDC) TAHU sahaja tersedia untuk perniagaan "
"berpusat di AS. Jika anda berada di luar AS, Stripe hanya menerima "
"pembayaran kad kredit ke baki Stripe anda (bukan terus ke crypto)."

msgid ""
"If you are in the US, you can use Stripe to receive crypto directly. If "
"outside, consider NOWPayments or CoinGate for direct crypto payouts."
msgstr ""
"Jika anda berada di AS, anda boleh menggunakan Stripe untuk menerima crypto "
"secara langsung. Jika di luar, pertimbangkan NOWPayments atau CoinGate untuk"
" pembayaran crypto langsung."

